OL,3,CPolice evacuate homes after
OL,4,C'suspicious device' found in Sheffield
OL,6,FResidents have been told to leave
OL,7,Ftheir homes after reports of a
OL,8,Fsuspicious device at a property in
OL,9,FSheffield.
OL,11,FSouth Yorkshire Police urged people to
OL,12,Favoid Washington Road, Sharrow,
OL,13,Ffollowing the discovery on Wednesday
OL,14,Fmorning.
OL,16,FA spokesperson said: "Emergency
OL,17,Fservices are in attendance and a 100m
OL,18,Fcordon has been put in place as a
OL,19,Fprecaution."
